<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 01:09:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>腕带使佩戴者能够通过自己的动作控制机械手</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/wristband-enables-wearers-to-control-a-robotic-hand-with-their-own-movements</link><description>麻省理工学院 (MIT) 工程师开发了一款超声波腕带，可以实时精确跟踪手部运动，用于机器人和虚拟现实控制。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/wristband-enables-wearers-to-control-a-robotic-hand-with-their-own-movements2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 01:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/wristband-enables-wearers-to-control-a-robotic-hand-with-their-own-movements</guid></item><item><title>研究发现，糖尿病药物二甲双胍会影响大脑：原因如下</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/diabetes-drug-metformin-affects-the-brain-study-finds-heres-how</link><description>您已经听说了 60 年的糖尿病药物刚刚揭示了一个秘密——它一直在作用于您的大脑。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/diabetes-drug-metformin-affects-the-brain-study-finds-heres-how2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 00:54:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/diabetes-drug-metformin-affects-the-brain-study-finds-heres-how</guid></item><item><title>替泽帕肽和伴随体重诱导药物的体重变化：随机临床试验的事后分析</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/weight-changes-with-tirzepatide-and-concomitant-weight-inducing-medications-post-hoc-analysis-of-randomized-clinical-trials</link><description>在三项随机对照试验中，替西帕肽与超重或肥胖成人中具有临床意义的体重减轻相关，即使在治疗期间开始同时服用减肥药物也是如此。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/weight-changes-with-tirzepatide-and-concomitant-weight-inducing-medications-post-hoc-analysis-of-randomized-clinical-trials.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 00:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/weight-changes-with-tirzepatide-and-concomitant-weight-inducing-medications-post-hoc-analysis-of-randomized-clinical-trials</guid></item><item><title>三重术前治疗可增强对软组织肉瘤的免疫力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/triple-pre-surgery-therapy-may-boost-immunity-against-soft-tissue-sarcoma</link><description>加州大学洛杉矶分校健康琼森综合癌症中心和斯坦福大学医学院的研究人员领导的临床前研究和临床试验的早期结果表明，在手术前将靶向放射治疗与实验性免疫增强药物 BO-112 和抗 PD-1 治疗相结合，可能有助于免疫系统对抗侵袭性软组织肉瘤。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/triple-pre-surgery-therapy-may-boost-immunity-against-soft-tissue-sarcoma.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 00:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/triple-pre-surgery-therapy-may-boost-immunity-against-soft-tissue-sarcoma</guid></item><item><title>揭开端粒酶的秘密，端粒酶是一种与衰老和癌症有关的酶</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unraveling-the-secrets-of-telomerase-an-enzyme-linked-to-aging-and-cancer</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 00:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unraveling-the-secrets-of-telomerase-an-enzyme-linked-to-aging-and-cancer</guid></item><item><title>X 射线激光器能够发现水中的临界点</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/x-ray-lasers-enable-the-discovery-of-a-critical-point-in-water</link><description>斯德哥尔摩大学的研究人员利用 X 射线激光确定了 -63 °C 左右和 1,000 个大气压下过冷水中是否存在临界点。较高温度和较低压力下的普通水会受到这个临界点的强烈影响，从而导致其奇怪性质的起源。研究结果是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/x-ray-lasers-enable-the-discovery-of-a-critical-point-in-water2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 23:54:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/x-ray-lasers-enable-the-discovery-of-a-critical-point-in-water</guid></item><item><title>颅内感染的 MRI 线索：区分细菌、病毒、真菌和寄生虫中枢神经系统疾病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mri-clues-to-intracranial-infection-differentiating-bacterial-viral-fungal-and-p